//Strings:- this data type store (characters/alphabet/names) name  and each  character contain 8 bit for store

module tab;
  reg [8*5:0] name="kunal_mishra";  // 8*5 = 40 only 5 character are store and rest of are ignore   
  
  initial $display("=name=%s", name);
  
endmodule 


K → 8 bits
u → 8 bits
n → 8 bits
a → 8 bits
l → 8 bits

Total = 5 × 8 = 40 bits (plus simulator-managed string overhead).
